Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:35.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N頭上的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在高度9500飛行中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,風速0.5至6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態 沒有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:39.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隨航機 不要掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:40.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行程序 CHECK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接駁主電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動回轉系統
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,打開平衡控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,發電系統轉為RG模式 啟動各控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,電離子容器壓力如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尚未達到3%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只能勉強達到極限壓力 我會盡量想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:01:59.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要解開鋼索 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,5秒前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:14.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,4~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,3~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,2~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,1~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,9000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,8500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,8000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,7500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,7000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,6500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,6000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米諾夫斯基粒子壓縮器正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,電離子推進力與預測值差別很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回轉系統也基本沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,震動比想像中的要輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,開始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是... 哥哥的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看啊 死神還真勤勞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮還真可憐呢 被這種瘟神纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 讓人同情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要剋死多少同伴才肯罷休？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,新手的隊長先生就像是來送死的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 軍 軍曹...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 有這種部下太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,軍曹...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！死神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長~ 隊長~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,頭痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 你在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,死神在打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,對手是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是07小隊那一夥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要買趁早 不快點的話就打完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,10點鐘方向 大概380米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 以前軍曹所在的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是全軍覆沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰說的這種無聊話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,07小隊太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是死神 就要像個死神的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,給我長眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓開 讓開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然3個一起上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙啊！你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在吵什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這是消遣活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,正在加深小隊間的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交流？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交流打架經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:36.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,07小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣的西部地區的後方支援怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 這就出動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 08小隊也要準備好能隨時出動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:48.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全員 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去 你們都回自己的崗位去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之 別給死神纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,新兵先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊的中傷罷了 別放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,眼看APSARAS計劃的第1階段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在諸位的同心協力之下完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS的完成在即
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,完成之後 地球圈的勢力圖就會被大大地改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利一定會在我們吉翁的旗幟下閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,為了光輝的吉翁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:51.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁萬歲~！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:03.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以德金公王才會將這項計劃交由我全權負責
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(是愛娜小姐)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(這可真是...)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(真漂亮 真是漂亮啊~)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就屬你最美麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的首次試飛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,意義重大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,帶給了我無比的驚嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,空調的狀態現在還差了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,出了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能享用美味的飲品 真是令人高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亞斯在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:55.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里·凱拉尼將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 讓開 讓出條路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亞斯 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多人面前 不要這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 沒關係的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:15.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你造出了不得了的玩具 我特地從歐洲趕了過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,玩具!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那個愛娜已經變得這麼有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上次見面時還只是個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女人真是可怕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凱拉尼大人也變得器宇不凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那種恭維說話不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,做我的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不幫那個執著於薩哈林之名的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你也能一生快快樂樂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,請別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的空氣好像很差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 沒趣的兄妹倆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在明明是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:35.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有那個人在 總是讓哥哥無法保持理智
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我若是哥哥的話早就教訓他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐為何會到這裏來？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,為了哥哥的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣說很奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要是哥哥的APSARAS完成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰火就會平息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:56.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那個無疑是件會奪去很多生命的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了薩哈林家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,從今以後 我也將和薩哈林家共存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 諾裏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尊嚴、名譽、血統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,薩哈林家的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是個人偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 山達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不駕駛MS了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能夠轉職
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞 你來代替我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,說 說什麼呢... 我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我來駕駛好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,作為機師...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己覺得不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能讓大家因我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還在說這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你所在部隊全軍覆沒的確是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可你被07小隊的傢伙戲弄一下就生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不就等於承認了自己是死神嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所 所以 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不干難道就沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個沒有種的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你也有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這種沒志氣的隊員我才不稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,適可而止 曹長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我所屬的部隊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全都在第3次出擊時全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不祥的第3次...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:07.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,留我在08小隊裏的話 大家都會因此而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不想駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:15.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你把同伴的死當成是自己背負的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是行動中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你的轉職請求是無法接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回你的崗位去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:35.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會破除掉那種無聊的迷信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有不妙的預感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明天最好也沒有戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想要活著的話 彼此間沒有信任怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是信賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,警報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是到達極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,遙測儀也有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聯絡各個部隊盡可能將防衛線擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,確保APSARAS的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,諾裏斯 告訴我機體的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 現在還看不出什麼特別的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 繼續測試負荷率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:56.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐 請不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙的目的到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:16.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山達斯 現在開始向376地區移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我來帶頭 你跟著我來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是討厭的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,寫遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖 膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,機體再次劇烈震動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 高度4000
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,超負荷嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,無法控制姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,急速下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把高度輸入操控電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,進入了聯邦的勢力圈 警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,高度沒有上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想辦法停止下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,散佈米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我到高空去聯絡基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,東北方的防衛線現在有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 已經開始了騷擾攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 基尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該讓愛娜撤出了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以放棄APSARAS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜的話應該能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是隨航機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時是成功阻止了下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好 愛娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,預備部隊也一起出動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,將APSARAS飛行路線上的聯邦的耳目引開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:50.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀呀 天才太過於自信的話 可沒有好結果的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:52.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:53.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姿勢控制器大致回復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,發信系統恢復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多是時候得回歐洲戰線去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙能用時就送去我那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是為了你這種人而造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 天才君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞 能測定敵人的位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,11點鐘方向 約2000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,現在卡蓮在追擊他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:31.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 敵人正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比是在引誘我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 哪裏不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什... 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 怎麼辦 追上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 請聽聽這些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(東面 25公里 佈防完畢)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(明白)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:04.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(保護好APSARAS...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(沿著叢林...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(要盡快掃清APSARAS的航路)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,由於有米諾夫斯基粒子在干擾 我聽不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看來敵人有東西正向這邊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 為何不用暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們在這裏伏擊那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全員降低態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西 真的會過來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,它正在過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 40秒後會經由東上空到達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它過去 靜觀其變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說這就是軍曹的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到氣壓震動 相當龐大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是MS的體積
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有復數個戰鬥機的引擎聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:16.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:19.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,測定射程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上清掃APSARAS的航路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋為什麼開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎... 怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,衝過來了 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,做了多餘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會死的 好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 軍... 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好... 好大...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼傢伙呀!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,諾裏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 愛娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,還能返航嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 愛娜小姐 請您撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我來掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁那時候撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會讓任何人死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼的鹵莽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:11.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 我... 才不是死神！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:27.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了？怎麼能輸 我... 我怎麼能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊 不停地射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊直到槍身過熱為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:42.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐 再接近會有危險 請您盡快撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好 山達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我還活著喔 軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 還活著...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,得 得救了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,總 總算沒事...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:27.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,迷信什麼的是能破除的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:30.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此信任的話就能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:21.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁新兵器的存在 對我軍產生了很大的衝擊
